  ],
  "remarks": "State Unitary Enterprise of the Lugansk People’s Republic “Lugansk Communications”, formerly known as State Unitary Enterprise of the Lugansk People’s Republic “Republican Digital Communication”, is a telecoms operator operating in the illegally occupied region of Ukraine of Luhansk. It was founded and is controlled by the so-called “Luhansk People’s Republic” authorities and is registered as a Russian legal entity.",
